title: Annual closing prices - Volkswagen shares 2013 to 2018
summary: This is a multi-line chart with 2 lines representing Common stock, and Preferred stock. The y axis denotes SOME LABEL and the x axis denotes Year.
Overall Common stock, and Preferred stock are gradually decreasing,  throughout the Year
The ranking of the lines from topmost to botommmost is as follows: 1. Common stock, and lastly, 2. Preferred stock.

The botommost line, Preferred stock,  has a mean of 160.21, and peaked at 2013.
Preferred stock reported the highest SOME LABEL about 204.15 in Year 2013
The minimum SOME LABEL about 133.35, occured at 2016 by Preferred stock.
The difference of SOME LABEL between Common stock and Preferred stock is smaller at Year 2018 compared to the Year 2013.
